WEBVTT

00:05:29.337 --> 00:05:35.000
He would say, "Education is an animal
that you have to overcome.

00:05:35.779 --> 00:05:39.101
With an education, you can survive.

00:05:39.838 --> 00:05:43.924
Education shall be your first husband."

00:05:44.557 --> 00:05:49.633
And with these words came in
his first big investment.

00:05:49.657 --> 00:05:50.932
I felt lucky!

00:05:51.627 --> 00:05:54.806
But I was missing something:

00:05:56.462 --> 00:05:57.613
my mother.

00:05:59.064 --> 00:06:01.555
My mother had been left
behind in the camp,